<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="container mt-4">
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="/images/shop-front.jpg" alt="Sam1 Flower Shop Storefront" class="img-fluid mb-4">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <p>Sam1 Flower Shop has been serving our community with beautiful floral arrangements since 1985. What started as a small family business has grown into a beloved local institution, known for our quality flowers and exceptional customer service.</p>
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>Our mission is to bring joy and beauty to our customers' lives through our stunning floral creations. We believe in the power of flowers to express emotions, celebrate milestones, and brighten everyday moments.</p>
                <h2>Our Team</h2>
                <p>Our team of skilled florists combines years of experience with a passion for creativity. Each arrangement is crafted with care and attention to detail, ensuring that every bouquet is a work of art.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>